These updates suggest active development and refinement of the e-commerce store's features.

User-Management-System.summary: The User-Management-System repository has experienced substantial activities from December 14th to December 18th, with multiple push events focused on implementing essential features. These updates indicate progress in building a comprehensive user management system.
